headline: Three Reasons to Avoid LMT and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Lockheed Martin currently trades at $481.80 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a middling return of 4.3%. This is close to the S&P 500’s 7% gain during that period.
